# Auto Pipeline Tab — Final Plan (v3)

YouTube Download → SRT Chapter Split → Style Rewrite trong 1 thẻ duy nhất.

---

## Architecture — 3-Phase Parallel Pipeline

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    INFO["get_video_info()"] --> P1

    subgraph P1["Phase 1 — PARALLEL"]
        DL_VID["⬇ Video (.mp4)"]
        DL_THUMB["🖼 Thumbnail"]
        DL_TRANS["📝 Transcript"]
    end

    DL_TRANS --> CLASSIFY["AI classify_script_type()"]
    CLASSIFY --> MISMATCH{"Mismatch?"}
    MISMATCH -->|yes| POPUP["⚠ Popup with video title"]
    MISMATCH -->|no| SPLIT
    POPUP --> SPLIT["split → verify → punctuate → save"]

    SPLIT --> P3
    DL_VID --> P3

    subgraph P3["Phase 3 — PARALLEL"]
        CUT["✂ Cut Video"]
        REWRITE["✍ Rewrite"]
    end

    style P1 fill:#1a3a1a,stroke:#4CAF50
    style P3 fill:#1a3a1a,stroke:#4CAF50
```

### Multi-URL Threading

| Mode | Phase 1 | Phase 2 | Phase 3 |
|------|---------|---------|---------|
| Single | 3 parallel tasks | Sequential | 2 parallel tasks |
| Independent (N URLs) | N×3 tasks | N parallel splits | N×2 tasks |
| Merge (N URLs, top/list only) | N×3 tasks | N parallel splits | 1 rewrite job |

UI: `Threads: [spinbox 1-5]` cho số video song song

