## Output Structure

```
{output_root}/{video_title}_[{videoID}]/
├── 01_download/           ← video, thumb, transcript
├── 02_chapters/           ← split chapter files + MERGED.txt
└── 03_rewrite/            ← rewritten chapters + FULL_SCRIPT.txt + _pipeline/
```

